_sText:
Hi, another one out!
this one is a sky/egyptian theme, as the screenshots suggest.
Theres around 17-18 traps and a few hidden nades around.

First thing coming to my mind writing this is mentioning the bridges from rock to rock, it's player clips inbetween the blocks wich means you don't have to jump from block to block you can walk :)

Other then that the files are embedded, it's got color correction, HDR Lightning and soundscapes so make sure you got that enabled for max experience!

The name is like it is because I couldent find a single name at all for this one so suck it up.

The map ended on a surprisingly low file size, 24 mb (6mb zipped) but then again Reacz textures did take 60% of the file size on my last map.

Feedback appreciated, hope you all enjoy!
